<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>Best stack for holiday gifting campaigns?</strong> Privy gift capture, Sequenzy guide and deadline orchestration, Klaviyo gift/self segments, Omnisend/Postscript final SMS, Yotpo gift UGC, collision calendar mandatory. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
